# StyleUp ERP — Project Context

StyleUp ERP is the admin dashboard for **StyleQuest**, a salon and beauty booking platform based in Kochi, Kerala. The backend is a separate NestJS service (`styleup-backend`). Never suggest backend code changes from this repo — only flag when an API contract change is needed.

## Stack

Vite 8, React 19, TypeScript strict, Tailwind v4 (CSS-first), shadcn/ui (radix-nova), TanStack Query/Table/Virtual, Zustand, react-router-dom, CASL, react-hook-form + Zod, calendarkit-basic, socket.io-client, i18next. Package manager: **pnpm only**.

## 19 Modules

| Folder | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `dashboard` | Overview KPIs and quick actions for operators |
| `user-management` | Platform end-user accounts (customers) |
| `merchant-management` | Salon/merchant onboarding and profiles |
| `staff-management` | Staff profiles, roles, and assignments per merchant |
| `service-catalog` | Individual services offered (cut, color, etc.) |
| `package-management` | Bundled service packages and pricing |
| `booking-management` | Appointment lifecycle (create, status, cancel) |
| `calendar-scheduling` | Staff/resource calendar and availability |
| `payments` | Transactions, refunds, and payment status |
| `promotions` | Discounts, coupons, and campaigns |
| `reviews` | Customer reviews and moderation |
| `messaging` | In-app chat between users and merchants |
| `notifications` | Push/email/SMS notification templates and logs |
| `loyalty` | Points, tiers, and reward programs |
| `media-library` | Shared images and assets for merchants |
| `reports-analytics` | Business reports and analytics dashboards |
| `system-configuration` | Global platform settings |
| `role-permission` | RBAC roles and permission assignments |
| `audit-logs` | Immutable admin action audit trail |

## Non-negotiables

- TypeScript **strict mode** always (`tsconfig.app.json`)
- No `any` without an inline justification comment
- **pnpm only** — never suggest npm/yarn commands or npm lockfiles
- Import alias `@/` maps to `src/`
